<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='375655' id='t-375655'>had this man not injured me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377061' id='t-377061'>had my genes been fed a different helping of experience.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380942' id='t-380942'>Who was I?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383155' id='t-383155'>Was I who I had been before the crash,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385972' id='t-385972'>before this road divided my life like the spine of an open book?</span>
